{"tid":2366570,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"TSM, 我們在寶島的家","createTime":"2021-01-14T15:08:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T15:15:04.000Z","uid":231905,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dc2503098cf0b6e42ef8f8bde16de242e2e80e9c","tid":2366570,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T15:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5NsOaqw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5NsOaqw.jpg&h=54ac9d66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我們在寶島的家：願人都尊台積電的名為聖。<br />\n願積電的晶圓降臨，願積電的晶片運行在本地，<br />\n如同雲端在天上。我們盼望的慢牛，<br />\n求積電天天賜給我們，又求饒恕等待回調的罪，<br />\n因為我們饒恕不願SH的人。<br />\n不叫我們遇見洪水地震，拯救我們脫離武統。<br />\n離開寶島的叛徒，定必受到制裁之火的懲罰。<br />\n因為2nm、3nm、5nm，<br />\n全是積電的恩賜，直到永遠。阿們。"},{"pid":"edfd3df930f43353c5cd9ca019c00ab011d1be83","tid":2366570,"uid":120629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T15:09:15.000Z","msg":"Let's say T<br />\nLet's say S<br />\nLet's say M<br />\nTSM TSM TSm"},{"pid":"4ac4fd63776edbb94fd96e919b07d40ee71e9057","tid":2366570,"uid":90640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T15:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949852ebbc3f5991d63f3da3738079b37bdef08c","tid":2366570,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T15:10:20.000Z","msg":"TSM -- 唯一信仰"},{"pid":"0a85851d69a032d076722847cec7c158d9a25d1e","tid":2366570,"uid":231905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T15:12:21.000Z","msg":"咁多位巴打，有冇信教？"},{"pid":"15996ae828610728cedb678b3275007280211199","tid":2366570,"uid":76747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T15:13:30.000Z","msg":"有人開PO<br />\n走先"},{"pid":"0853a6296fa7c5e3de19cb82070051af607679ad","tid":2366570,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15996ae828610728cedb678b3275007280211199","t